<h2 id="q-how-do-i-install-the-toho-c-mod" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#q-how-do-i-install-the-toho-c-mod"><span><font color=cyan>Q: How do I install the TOHO-C mod?</font></span></a></h2>
<p>A: You don’t need to install anything for the TOHO-C mod if you’re a player. Since it’s a host-only mod, as long as the host has it enabled, everyone can enjoy the new content without having to download anything.</p>
<h2 id="q-what-does-toho-c-stand-for-and-what-s-different-about-this-mod" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#q-what-does-toho-c-stand-for-and-what-s-different-about-this-mod"><span><font color=purple>Q: What does TOHO-C stand for, and what’s different about this mod?</font></span></a></h2>
