<h2 id="q-do-players-need-to-install-the-mod-too-or-only-the-host" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#q-do-players-need-to-install-the-mod-too-or-only-the-host"><span><font color=red>Q: Do players need to install the mod too, or only the host?</font></span></a></h2>
